    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Visual works or parts of works made of minutely faceted and riveted studs generally made of steel; often used for brooches, buckles, bottons, and swordhilts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
